metadata.name: rabbit
metadata.description:
In general, you are very lucky and have a lucky fate. The Mayan Rabbit symbolizes luck and abundance, just like in China, and has similar characteristics in Chinese culture and astrology. Your standout feature is your comfortable and easy way through the "real" world. You can succeed easily and always land on your feet.

Your mind has also benefited from the abundance of the Rabbit. You have a mind that never gives up and needs constant stimulation. That's why you love to read, talk and communicate with people on any subject. In general, we can call you an abundance magnet. Your highly developed aesthetic perception, bright mind and humorous demeanor enable you to live a pleasant life. Your magic secret to a healthy life is to have the ability to have a light heart and a good sense of humor even in the toughest times. In addition, personal characteristics include energetic, wandering, bored.
